      <title>土耳其投资者追逐收益率达 50% 的利基债券，无视其他债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/turkish-investors-chasing-niche-bond-yielding-50-ignore-others</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其的高通胀使得与央行利率挂钩的利基债券成为新星，这使得海外投资者没有理由购买市场上的其他债券。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-12/turkish-investors-chasing-niche-bond-yielding-50-ignore-others</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Sep 2024 05:30:01 GMT</pubDate>
